data.description: Welcome home, to this beautiful single family home. This property features 975 SqFt in living space, and a spacious 7,270 SqFt lot. The formal entry leads to a cozy living room, open to a tastefully remodeled kitchen with quartz counter tops and vinyl flooring throughout. Down the hallway, you will find 3 spacious bedrooms and 2 beautifully remodeled bathrooms. A few other  upgrades include central AC, water filtration system, new flooring throughout, newer interior paint, new interior doors, toilets and more. The spacious  back yard is perfect for entertaining or ADU and the short distance to the park,  freeways and shopping is just the cherry on top! Definitely a must see!
